Rating: 4
Added 1/4 tsp of cayenne on the advice of previous reviewer, made this a night ahead of a bridal shower luncheon; it was a huge hit. The shower color theme was orange, so this was an extra special treat. The contrast of the green chives was perfect. It is so easy to make now that one can purchase shredded carrots. B.J. Harrick

