I would definitely not make this again. I've never encountered such a bomb of a recipe on Epicurious before. Part of the problem is the name. Rather than a "salad," it's more like a slaw, really, which could be ok, I guess, but the carrots and yogurt don't taste good together (at all) and the whole thing is a very unappetizing pink/orange color. I'm not even going to serve it.